  "original_title": "\u0db1\u0dd2\u0dc0\u0dcf\u0dc3 \u0d85\u0db8\u0dcf\u0dad\u0dca\u200d\u0dba\u0dcf\u0d82\u0dc1\u0dba\u0dda \u0db8\u0dc4\u0da2\u0db1 \u0daf\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dba\u0da7 \u0dc0\u0dcf\u0dc3\u0dd4\u0dad\u0dca \u0d87\u0dc0\u0dd2\u0dad\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Vasut has come to the Public Day of the Ministry of Housing",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "It is special that former minister Vasudeva Nanayakkara, who was an independent member of the opposition, also participated in the Public Day of the Ministry of Urban Development and Housing, which was held today (22) under the chairmanship of Minister Prasanna Ranatunga.",
        "Mr. Nanayakkara presented a problem faced by the people of Nugegoda area to Minister Prasanna Ranatunga.",
        "Mr. Prasanna Ranatunga took steps to solve the problem presented by the MP Vasudeva Nanayakkara within a few minutes.",
        "The presidents, directors general and general managers of 21 institutions under the Ministry of Urban Development and Housing participated in this public day.",
        "Minister Prasanna Ranatunga, who made a statement at the beginning of the People's Day, informed the heads of the institutions to provide solutions to the problems presented by the people on a weekly basis and submit a report to him that same week.",
        "The minister said that the people should never be harassed and emphasized that the officials should ensure that those issues are not presented to the next public day."
      ],
